== Mentoring 

I work with students on a meaningful academic research experience. Current student mentorship include:

=== Undergraduate research awards

- Working with Dr. Xie, one Public Relations major is awarded the College of Communication Arts and Sciences Undergraduate Research Award. 10/2025

- Working with Dr. Xie, one Advertising Management major is awarded the College of Communication Arts and Sciences Undergraduate Research Award. 10/2025


=== Undergraduate research projects

- Towards a generative AI chatbot in wellbeing.  Research team with 2 advertising management majors. Our team is working with an entrepreneurship incubator program with the vision to patent and commercialize our product.

- Integrating Generative AI in internal communication: Influence on employee emotions and engagement. 1 public relations major.

- You can’t pour from an empty cup: How communication training impacts medical students’ empathy towards self and patients. 1 exploratory major.

- The boundary spanning function of public relations: Communication excellence of caddies as semi-internal publics in internal communication. 1 advertising management major.


